ets-release-date-for-new-album-the-2020-experience.html|title=Justin Timberlake sets release date for new album 'The 20/20 Experience'|publisher=Hearst Magazines UK|date=2013-01-25|deadurl=no|accessdate=2013-01-25|archive-date=2015-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706191314/http://www.digitalspy.com/music/news/a453822/justin-timberlake-sets-release-date-for-new-album-the-2020-experience.html}}</ref>

